+    /* MP6 native port -- docs/M2D_MENUS.md. Real, unpatched original decomp
+     * bug (not a decompilation error -- this exact typo shape, reusing the
+     * same GXAttr identifier for both arguments instead of the GXVtxFmt
+     * slot selector the first parameter actually wants, is a classic
+     * copy-paste mistake): every OTHER GXSetVtxAttrFmt call in this same
